title.label: Great game, but a couple problems

content.label: The game is pretty fun to play and is really addictive, but with the many ads it can be pretty frustrating especially with difficult levels.(and there wasn't an option to pay to remove them either)  But ads weren’t the only problem....around level 60 I see many problems where the screen messes up and I can still see the title screen and it won’t let me tap at times. Also on some of the time levels after I fail a level and go to retry, the timer from the previous attempt is still running and it fails the current try. So far I’m on level 70 and these are the only issues I’ve seen so far. This game can easily have a higher rating if these issues are fixed. But besides that I definitely enjoy the game and I find it to be an excellent time-killer, and I would definitely recommend it to other people.👍👍
